\c 133
\s Kunaka korudo pakati pehama
\d Rwiyo rworwendo; rwaDhavhidhi.
\p
\v 1 Tarirai, kunaka kwazvo nokufadza kwazvo kana hama dzichigara pamwe chete norugare.
\v 2 Zvakafanana namafuta anokosha ari pamusoro, anoyerera pandebvu, idzo ndebvu dzaAroni; anoburukira kusvikira pamipendero yenguvo dzake.
\v 3 Zvakafanana nedova reHerimoni, rinoburukira pamakomo eZiyoni; nokuti ndipo Jehovha paakaraira kuropafadza kwake, ndihwo upenyu husingaperi.
